{
  "stem": "13623.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I was barely 14 at the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I should have been able to-- to jump, but I couldn't even walk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Some of my friends that I used to help with food, when I used to sort of bring the food into the camp from-- from the kitchen that I used to work in, they were walking alongside me, took one of my arms and put it on-- on each of their shoulders, and I would-- I walked into camp that way.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We came into the camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We were all assigned to barracks where we slept.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We did not work in that camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We were warehoused, for a better word.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Epidemic broke out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Typhus.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Cholera.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Where people had very-- they were burning up from the temperature, the high temperature, and they would-- people would drop.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "It was very common to see dead bodies all over, all around you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "We were sleeping in those carts, like-- like those shelves, like 10-- 10 to a cart, like-- They used to come in once a day with a watered down, what we called kolorabi soup.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "A lot of people were very weak.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They couldn't get down to-- to get their soup.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "So they would go around-- fellow prisoners would go around with a-- with a can, it looked like what we know today as like a garbage can, with the soup was in it with a ladle.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "We had our plates.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And if you just held your hand out, as weak as you were, they would pour a ladle of soup into the-- into your plate.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And that continued.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Naturally I was hungry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "That-- that soup was not enough.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
